<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3184] Xmx setting in pom to use for tests/surefire does not appear to work</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3184</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I was running intense version of TestRollingRestart and changing the Xmx setting in our pom file wasn&apos;t changing anything.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;What we have now is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;            &amp;lt;argLine&amp;gt;-enableassertions&amp;lt;/argLine&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;argLine&amp;gt;-Xmx1400m&amp;lt;/argLine&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But on process listing (and through experimentation with my tests), only -enableassertions is used.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, changing to below and it worked:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;            &amp;lt;argLine&amp;gt;-enableassertions -Xmx1400m&amp;lt;/argLine&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Just wanted to open a jira and see if i&apos;m missing something from someone with more maven experience.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
